    "search_terms": "find distance between points multiple subparts distance formula",
    "question": {
      "text": "Find the distance between the points $A$ and $B$ in the following:\n\n(i) $A(a+b,b-a)$, $B(a-b,a+b)$\n\n(ii) $A(1,-1)$, $B\\left(-\\frac{1}{2},\\frac{1}{2}\\right)$\n\n(iii) $A(8,-2)$, $B(3,-6)$\n\n(iv) $A(a+b,a-b)$, $B(a-b,a-b)$",
