    "solution": {
      "text": "Use the distance formula.",
      "image": "#"
    },
    "solution_steps": [
      "Step 1: Using the distance formula:",
      "$d=\\sqrt{(x_2-x_1)^2+(y_2-y_1)^2}$",
      "where $(x_1,y_1)$ and $(x_2,y_2)$ are the coordinates of the two points.",
      "Step 2: Part (i):",
      "$A(a+b,b-a),\\ B(a-b,a+b)$",
      "$d=\\sqrt{[(a-b)-(a+b)]^2+[(a+b)-(b-a)]^2}$",
      "$=\\sqrt{(-2b)^2+(2a)^2}$",
      "$=\\sqrt{4b^2+4a^2}$",
      "$=2\\sqrt{a^2+b^2}$",
      "Distance $=2\\sqrt{a^2+b^2}$",
      "Step 3: Part (ii):",
      "$A(1,-1),\\ B\\left(-\\frac{1}{2},\\frac{1}{2}\\right)$",
      "$d=\\sqrt{\\left(-\\frac{1}{2}-1\\right)^2+\\left(\\frac{1}{2}-(-1)\\right)^2}$",
      "$=\\sqrt{\\left(-\\frac{3}{2}\\right)^2+\\left(\\frac{3}{2}\\right)^2}$",
      "$=\\sqrt{\\frac{9}{4}+\\frac{9}{4}}$",
      "$=\\sqrt{\\frac{9}{2}}$",
      "$=\\frac{3}{\\sqrt{2}}=\\frac{3\\sqrt{2}}{2}$",
      "Distance $=\\frac{3\\sqrt{2}}{2}$",
      "Step 4: Part (iii):",
      "$A(8,-2),\\ B(3,-6)$",
      "$d=\\sqrt{(3-8)^2+(-6-(-2))^2}$",
      "$=\\sqrt{(-5)^2+(-4)^2}$",
      "$=\\sqrt{25+16}$",
      "$=\\sqrt{41}$",
      "Distance $=\\sqrt{41}$",
      "Step 5: Part (iv):",
      "$A(a+b,a-b),\\ B(a-b,a-b)$",
      "$d=\\sqrt{[(a-b)-(a+b)]^2+[(a-b)-(a-b)]^2}$",
      "$=\\sqrt{(-2b)^2+0^2}$",
      "$=\\sqrt{4b^2}$",
      "$=2b$",
      "Distance $=2b$",
      "Final Answer: $(i)\\ 2\\sqrt{a^2+b^2},\\ (ii)\\ \\frac{3\\sqrt{2}}{2},\\ (iii)\\ \\sqrt{41},\\ (iv)\\ 2b$"
