      "text": "Using distance formula, show that the points $A$, $B$ and $C$ are collinear:\n\n(i) $A(-1,-1)$, $B(2,3)$, $C(8,11)$\n\n(ii) $A(-4,-2)$, $B(-1,1)$, $C(1,3)$",
