      "$AM=\\sqrt{\\left(\\frac{5}{2}-3\\right)^2+\\left(-\\frac{3}{2}-4\\right)^2}$",
      "Step 5: Simplify:",
      "$=\\sqrt{\\left(-\\frac{1}{2}\\right)^2+\\left(-\\frac{11}{2}\\right)^2}$",
      "$=\\sqrt{\\frac{1}{4}+\\frac{121}{4}}$",
      "Step 6: Further simplification:",
      "$=\\sqrt{\\frac{122}{4}}$",
      "$=\\frac{\\sqrt{122}}{2}$",
